---
title: Creamy Rosé Chicken Tender Tortellini  with Roasted Red Pepper Pesto
description: This one is just like your favourite restaurant's cheesy tortellini! The creamy rosé sauce coats every piece of pillowy pasta and the gooey mozzarella cheese makes for an unforgettable takeout fake-out.

